        "custom_liquid": "{% comment %}\n  TryScent listicle — page chrome hider.\n\n  Hides the theme's header, footer, and announcement bar on the current page only.\n  Custom Liquid sections only render on pages they're added to, so the CSS\n  scopes itself naturally — other pages are unaffected.\n\n  USAGE:\n  1. Online Store → Themes → Customize → open the page that has the listicle.\n  2. Add section → Custom Liquid\n  3. Drag this section to the TOP of the page (above everything else).\n  4. Paste this entire file into the textarea.\n  5. Save.\n\n  If something on your theme isn't getting hidden, paste its selector into the\n  rule below. To find selectors: right-click the element → Inspect.\n{% endcomment %}\n\n<style>\n  /* OS 2.0 theme groups (Dawn, Sense, Refresh, Studio, Crave, Origin, Trade,\n     Publisher, Colorblock, Taste, Ride, Spotlight, etc.) */\n  .shopify-section-group-header-group,\n  .shopify-section-group-footer-group,\n  .shopify-section-group-announcement-group,\n  .shopify-section-group-aside-group,\n\n  /* Vintage themes + common explicit IDs/classes */\n  #shopify-section-header,\n  #shopify-section-footer,\n  #shopify-section-announcement-bar,\n  .shopify-section-header,\n  .shopify-section-footer,\n  .shopify-section-announcement-bar,\n\n  /* Direct element fallbacks */\n  body > header,\n  body > footer,\n  .site-header,\n  .site-footer,\n  .header-wrapper,\n  .footer-wrapper,\n  .announcement-bar,\n  .announcement,\n\n  /* Newsletter popups & promo banners that float */\n  .promo-bar,\n  .header__promo,\n  .top-bar,\n  .topbar,\n  #topbar,\n  [class*=\"topbar\"],\n  [id*=\"topbar\"],\n  .shopify-section[id*=\"topbar\"],\n\n  /* Sale / countdown / timer banner sections (Lönedagsrea, BFCM, etc.) */\n  [class*=\"countdown\"],\n  [class*=\"timer-bar\"],\n  [class*=\"sale-bar\"],\n  [class*=\"salebar\"],\n  [class*=\"payday\"],\n  [class*=\"lonedag\"],\n  [class*=\"lönedag\"],\n  [id*=\"countdown\"],\n  [id*=\"timer-bar\"],\n  [id*=\"payday\"],\n  [id*=\"salebar\"],\n  .shopify-section[id*=\"countdown\"],\n  .shopify-section[id*=\"timer\"],\n  .shopify-section[id*=\"payday\"],\n  .shopify-section[id*=\"sale-bar\"],\n  .shopify-section[id*=\"promo\"],\n  .shopify-section[id*=\"banner\"]:not([id*=\"hero\"]) {\n    display: none !important;\n    visibility: hidden !important;\n    height: 0 !important;\n    margin: 0 !important;\n    padding: 0 !important;\n    overflow: hidden !important;\n  }\n\n  /* Reset main content offsets so the listicle starts at the very top */\n  body,\n  main,\n  #MainContent,\n  .main-content,\n  .page-width {\n    padding-top: 0 !important;\n    margin-top: 0 !important;\n  }\n\n  /* Remove default body padding some themes set for sticky headers */\n  body {\n    padding-top: 0 !important;\n  }\n</style>",
